OL,3,CFootball clubs urged to put away nets
OL,4,Cto stop animals getting stuck
OL,6,FThe RSPCA has called on football clubs
OL,7,Fand the public to help save animals by
OL,8,Fputting away nets following the end of
OL,9,Fthe season.
OL,11,FThe charity said it received 1,355
OL,12,Freports in 2024 of animals getting
OL,13,Fentangled in netting, with almost half
OL,14,Fof them in the peak months of May,
OL,15,FJune and July.
OL,17,FThe charity's scientific officer said
OL,18,Funattended football and other netting
OL,19,Fcan trap, injure and kill wildlife and
OL,20,Fpets.
