OL,3,CFootball clubs urged to put away nets
OL,4,Cto stop animals getting stuck
OL,6,FRebecca Machin said: "It's really
OL,7,Fimportant to put nets safely away when
OL,8,Fthey're not being used after the game
OL,9,Fis done.
OL,11,F"The problem is so serious that during
OL,12,Flast year's peak months, we dealt with
OL,13,F100 incidents of netting-entangled
OL,14,Ffoxes - mostly cubs.
OL,16,F"But it's not just foxes that are
OL,17,Faffected; other wild mammals like
OL,18,Fhedgehogs and deer, and even domestic
OL,19,Fpet mammals - including cats, can
OL,20,Fbecome potentially fatally entangled.
