OL,3,CFootball clubs urged to put away nets
OL,4,Cto stop animals getting stuck
OL,6,F"But amid a difficult period for many
OL,7,Fanimals, when netting reports
OL,8,Ftypically spike, people have the power
OL,9,Fto make a real difference."
OL,11,FThe charity was also called out more
OL,12,Fthan 1,500 times to birds getting
OL,13,Ftrapped.
OL,15,FOf the 263 wild animals that got
OL,16,Fcaught in nets, foxes (172) were the
OL,17,Fmost common, followed by deer (43) and
OL,18,Fhedgehogs.
