OL,3,CFootball clubs urged to put away nets
OL,4,Cto stop animals getting stuck
OL,6,FIn 2024 there were ten incidents of
OL,7,Fentangled animals in Northamptonshire,
OL,8,F13 in Bedfordshire, and 21 in
OL,9,FHertfordshire.
OL,11,FThe numbers were even greater in
OL,12,FNorfolk and Suffolk, where there were
OL,13,F49 incidents, while there were seven
OL,14,Fincidents in Cambridgeshire and 41
OL,15,Fcases in Essex.
OL,17,FThe charity's advice to the public is
OL,18,Fthat if a small animal is found caught
OL,19,Fup in netting but is uninjured, the
OL,20,Ffastest way to help it is to gently
OL,21,Fand carefully disentangle the animal.
